MatchedRegions.transcript: The EHR SQL dataset consists of 24,000 questions to SQL pairs, frequently asked on structured EHR data.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: The questions were collected from a poll conducted at a university hospital and more than 200 hospital staff, including doctors, nurses, insurance review staff, infection control staff, and more participated in the poll.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: The label SQL queries are linked to two open source EHR databases, Mimic 3 and EICU.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: The unique challenges of the dataset are, first, we have a wide range of real-world questions frequently asked on structured EHR data.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: From retrieving a patient's test results, to summing of a patient's total hospital cost, and calculating the survival rate of a certain group of patients, the questions in the dataset reflect the diverse needs of staff in the hospital.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: Second, time is very important in healthcare.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: To reflect that, we templatize time and combine them with the questions to make the data set more realistic.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: Lastly, we have unanswerable questions that were collected together from the poll.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: The questions were unanswerable because they were either ambiguous or went beyond the database schemas.

MatchedRegion.Text: FAQ on structured EHR data collected from a poll at a university hospital
SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU

MatchedRegions.transcript: These questions are later used to test the trustworthiness of text to SQL models.

SQL queries linked to MIMIC-III and elCU
